/* Initialization Code*/
variable.closes = []

variable.sum = []
variable.value = 0

////////////
variable.prevClose = NaN
variable.prevMax = NaN
variable.prevMin = NaN
variable.volumeArr = []
variable.minVols = []
variable.maxVols = []

variable.vola = []
variable.c_plus = []
variable.c_minus = []

variable.dem = []
variable.sup = []

variable.anp = []
variable.sentiRaw = []

variable.suppyE = 0
variable.demandE = 0
variable.value = 0
variable.vader = 0
variable.V_senti = 0

/* Loop Code */
// Gopalakrishnan Range Index, or GAPO
let pLength = 5


let candle = record.current // Create everything from candles data
let highest = 0
let lowest = 0
let gapo = 0

variable.highs.push(candle.max)
variable.lows.push(candle.min)
if (variable.highs.length > pLength) {
    variable.highs.splice(0, 1)     // keep array at maximum length
    variable.lows.splice(0, 1)

    highest = Math.max(...variable.highs)
    lowest = Math.min(...variable.lows)

    gapo = Math.log(highest - lowest) / Math.log(pLength)
}

variable.value = isFinite(gapo) ? gapo : 0

/* Initialization Code*/
variable.highs = []
variable.lows = []

variable.value = 0

/* Initialization Code*/
variable.closes = []
variable.opens = []

variable.prevEma = 0

variable.value = 0
variable.hist = 0

// T3 Velocity
// A type of rate of change oscillator made of 2 T3 Moving averages
// It compares the momentum of the 2 curves between the current and the previous period.
// The first curve is calculated upon the period and the complete factor ("vFactor" 
//parameter) and the second one with an half of this factor.
const pLength = 14
const t3hot = 1
const normPer = 20

let candle = record.current // Create everything from candles data
let alpha = t3hot
let source = candle.close


//Calculate first T3
let c1 = -alpha * alpha * alpha
let c2 = 3 * alpha * alpha + 3 * alpha * alpha * alpha
let c3 = -6 * alpha * alpha - 3 * alpha - 3 * alpha * alpha * alpha
let c4 = 1 + 3 * alpha + alpha * alpha * alpha + 3 * alpha * alpha

let alpha1 = 2.0 / (2.0 + (pLength - 1.0) / 2.0)

let t30 = source, t31 = source
let t32 = source, t33 = source
let t34 = source, t35 = source

t30 = variable.t30prev + alpha1 * (source - variable.t30prev)
t31 = variable.t31prev + alpha1 * (t30 - variable.t31prev)
t32 = variable.t32prev + alpha1 * (t31 - variable.t32prev)
t33 = variable.t33prev + alpha1 * (t32 - variable.t33prev)
t34 = variable.t34prev + alpha1 * (t33 - variable.t34prev)
t35 = variable.t35prev + alpha1 * (t34 - variable.t35prev)
let T3_1 = c1 * t35 + c2 * t34 + c3 * t33 + c4 * t32


// calculate second T3
alpha = alpha / 2
c1 = -alpha * alpha * alpha
c2 = 3 * alpha * alpha + 3 * alpha * alpha * alpha
c3 = -6 * alpha * alpha - 3 * alpha - 3 * alpha * alpha * alpha
c4 = 1 + 3 * alpha + alpha * alpha * alpha + 3 * alpha * alpha
//let alpha1 = 2.0 / (2.0 + (pLength - 1.0) / 2.0)

let t30_2 = source, t31_2 = source
let t32_2 = source, t33_2 = source
let t34_2 = source, t35_2 = source

t30_2 = variable.t30prev2 + alpha1 * (source - variable.t30prev2)
t31_2 = variable.t31prev2 + alpha1 * (t30_2 - variable.t31prev2)
t32_2 = variable.t32prev2 + alpha1 * (t31_2 - variable.t32prev2)
t33_2 = variable.t33prev2 + alpha1 * (t32_2 - variable.t33prev2)
t34_2 = variable.t34prev2 + alpha1 * (t33_2 - variable.t34prev2)
t35_2 = variable.t35prev2 + alpha1 * (t34_2 - variable.t35prev2)
let T3_2 = c1 * t35_2 + c2 * t34_2 + c3 * t33_2 + c4 * t32_2

////////////////////////////////
variable.value = T3_1 - T3_2        // final output value


// this section currently does nothing in SA as there is no dynamic colour selection allowable for plots
let smax = 0
let smin = 0
let sto = 0

variable.normArray.push(variable.value)
if (variable.normArray.length > normPer) {
    variable.normArray.splice(0, 1)

    smax = Math.max(...variable.normArray)
    smin = Math.min(...variable.normArray)

    sto = 100 * (variable.value - smin) / (smax - smin)
}


// save values for next iteration
variable.t30prev = t30
variable.t31prev = t31
variable.t32prev = t32
variable.t33prev = t33
variable.t34prev = t34
variable.t35prev = t35

variable.t30prev2 = t30_2
variable.t31prev2 = t31_2
variable.t32prev2 = t32_2
variable.t33prev2 = t33_2
variable.t34prev2 = t34_2
variable.t35prev2 = t35_2

//console.log(" *** ")
//console.log("close: ", candle.close)
//console.log("T3_1: ", T3_1)
//console.log("T3_2: ", T3_2)
//console.log(" ")

/* Initialization Code*/

/* Loop Code */
// HLC Trend by quantum8
const lenClose = 5
const lenHigh = 30
const lenLow = 13


const candle = record.current // Create everything from candles data

////////////////////////////////////
variable.highArr.push(candle.max)
variable.lowArr.push(candle.min)
variable.closeArr.push(candle.close)

let smaHigh = candle.max
let smaLow = candle.min
let smaClose = candle.close

if (variable.highArr.length > lenHigh) {
    variable.highArr.splice(0, 1)
}

if (variable.lowArr.length > lenLow) {
    variable.lowArr.splice(0, 1)
}

if (variable.closeArr.length > lenClose) {
    variable.closeArr.splice(0, 1)
}

smaHigh = variable.highArr.reduce((a, b) => (a + b)) / variable.highArr.length
smaLow = variable.lowArr.reduce((a, b) => (a + b)) / variable.lowArr.length
smaClose = variable.closeArr.reduce((a, b) => (a + b)) / variable.closeArr.length


let ma_CH = smaClose - smaHigh
let ma_LC = smaLow - smaClose

let fill_Color = ma_CH > ma_LC ? 1 : -1

let bg_Color = ma_CH >= ma_LC ? ma_CH < 0 && ma_CH < variable.closeHigh ? 0 : 1 : ma_LC < 0 && ma_LC < variable.lowClose ? 0 : -1

variable.closeHigh = ma_CH
variable.lowClose = ma_LC
variable.bgFill = bg_Color

/* Initialization Code*/
variable.highArr = []
variable.lowArr = []
variable.closeArr = []


variable.closeHigh = 0
variable.lowClose = 0

variable.bgFill = 0
